text:
Storm brings snow to places on East Coast that haven't seen it in years

A large winter storm hit the Carolinas to Maine, dumping snow in areas that haven't seen it in decades. Thursday, some could also see freezing cold temperatures and strong winds. Blizzard warnings and states of emergency were in effect.

twitter.title: ‘RelationShep’ recap: Shep Rose finds out what happens when 5 women kiss and tell
twitter.description: On the third episode of Bravo’s “RelationShep,” which aired Monday, December 18, 2017, Shep Rose goes on his first dates with the five women he’s brought back to Charleston, South Carolina, from Los Angeles, California, New York City, New York, Austen and Dallas, Texas. Things get a little dicey for the Hilton Head Island, South Carolina, native and “Southern Charm” star when the women start to compare notes on the attention he’s given them individually.
